modName: Max out alchemy smithing and enchanting
descriptionHtml:
This is a simple script that will allow you to max out the alchemy, smithing & enchanting skills and add the perks.

i used this because you only get 50 perks in game, and i didnt want to waste them on \"job\" skills. 

everything else is untouched. 

install = drag the text file to your skyrim .DIR
ingame console = 
bat syntax1985

Enjoy!!
author: Syntax1985
